# Keep the Docker build context minimal — only what the Dockerfile's
# `COPY Cargo.toml Cargo.lock` and `COPY crates` instructions read.
*

!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!crates
!Dockerfile

# Build artefacts inside `crates` must still be excluded — rebuilding
# them inside the container is the whole point.
crates/*/target/
crates/dux-web-browser/pkg/
crates/dux-web-browser/dist/
target/
